headline: AutoZone to Release First Quarter Fiscal 2026 Earnings December 9, 2025
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., Nov. 19, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE: AZO), the leading retailer and distributor of automotive replacement parts and accessories in the Americas, will release results for its first quarter ended Saturday, November 22, 2025, before market open on Tuesday, December 9, 2025.
